# 📊 Final Findings Report

Key Findings:

* Users appreciated the all-in-one app concept
* Vendor availability needs improvement
* Navigation and UI were positively received
* Entertainment and content categories need expansion
* Better onboarding can improve retention
* More active services can improve engagement

Recommendations:

* Increase vendor onboarding
* Improve app performance and UX
* Expand category coverage
* Add more user engagement features
* Continue feedback validation process

Final Deliverable:
Consolidated internship findings and recommendations based on verified user feedback.
